{"id": 2373, "genre": 1001, "title": "工作会议里的哪些环节会让你身心俱疲掉血一百点？", "description": "每个环节！说到这我必须得展开讲讲。（题图来自：视觉中国 © Ikon Images）", "record_count": 2663, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/2018052416594151HsAG6Cov3xWBRZ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-05-28T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 284177, "content": "很多人都在一起的时候我就不去了，我们的生活方式是什么时候回来呀，我们的生活方式是什么时候回来呀。。。。。。不过现在也可以有好收获每周吃两班同学一起加油去看一下自己的生活中最精彩瞬间天咯看了图图图图图图图图", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1358482}, {"id": 284181, "content": "比上课还累", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1349163}, {"id": 285207, "content": "整天开小会谈论别人哪里哪里不好，说自己哪里哪里好，做这些系统体系小菜一碟，结果反正也是都没有做！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649945}, {"id": 284186, "content": "结束了和没开一样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1358500}, {"id": 283676, "content": "会前要准备精美的 PPT，用的时间比开会还长", "image": null, "praise_count": 251, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 283677, "content": "大部分讨论明明可以点对点交流，但所有人都要坐这听着", "image": null, "praise_count": 525, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 283678, "content": "每周讨论同样的问题，同样的没有结果", "image": null, "praise_count": 73, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 283679, "content": "头脑风暴啥的，会前没人准备，会上冷场现想", "image": null, "praise_count": 302, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 283680, "content": "时间长且内容空洞，大家滔滔不绝但都是空话", "image": null, "praise_count": 200, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 284960, "content": "明明在讨论一个问题，然后有些大佬能想到一个八杆子远的另一件事，就开始说另一件事，说了20分钟以后再扯回来，会议记录很难做啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1360870}, {"id": 284202, "content": "每个人都说说自己的想法...", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 529159}, {"id": 284465, "content": "跑题！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359185}, {"id": 283955, "content": "讨论到最后得出的结论，在后续工作中一直被推翻。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 322, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198306}, {"id": 283956, "content": "一群人围一起猜boss会喜欢哪个方案，而boss不在现场", "image": null, "praise_count": 126, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1328801}, {"id": 283957, "content": "时间长，没有中心点，更无结果，浪费时间。", "image": null, "praise_count": 146, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1357345}, {"id": 283958, "content": "接下来我只说一点，随后漫漫人生路开讲", "image": null, "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1355755}, {"id": 283959, "content": "2分钟就能阐述完的事情，啰啰嗦嗦重复举例半个小时", "image": null, "praise_count": 202, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 832055}, {"id": 283960, "content": "谈虚又臭又长，谈实又会暴露不了解情况的事实", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1327060}, {"id": 283962, "content": "涉及部门多、人员多的时候，需要协调沟通太麻烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1357399}, {"id": 283963, "content": "每个人都说这个需要请示下老板！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595118}, {"id": 283964, "content": "说是头脑风暴，结果3分钟之后开始扯淡。明明可以早上做完的事情，因为对接人早上不来，总是要拖到加班搞定。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1159478}, {"id": 283966, "content": "空洞的内容和交流, 什么也没决定, 走出会议室感觉跟没开一样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 283317}, {"id": 283967, "content": "漫长的会议然后并没有讨论出解决方案", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 482668}, {"id": 283968, "content": "只谈问题，不谈解决方法。", "image": null, "praise_count": 87, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1326918}, {"id": 283969, "content": "老生常谈的互联网思维", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1338463}, {"id": 283970, "content": "面面俱到，面面不到位", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 899562}, {"id": 283971, "content": "上次会议的决议内容迟迟没有解决，最终演化成各部门的撕逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 926806}, {"id": 283974, "content": "过了两个小时，被告知还要再来一个小时，结果又是两个小时！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970221}, {"id": 283975, "content": "出差半年", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 500778}, {"id": 283976, "content": "东西越改越差，说好是来提意见的会议，却发现老板只听得进他想听的话", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 283977, "content": "假大空，然后还要输出会议纪要，并没人看，频率超级高。某些会，双周一次，感觉刚开完，又开会了", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1194744}, {"id": 283978, "content": "会前没人准备，会议过程中不断在做信息同步的工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 821455}, {"id": 283979, "content": "会前不说会议主题；会中没有总结统一；会后没有会议纪要", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1356202}, {"id": 283980, "content": "没有重点，时间长，讨论的事项不是跟每个人相关。没气氛", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1084360}, {"id": 285516, "content": "项目的思考路线不是for用户 or for 项目本身 而是for老板 一堆人都否定 老板觉得好 就执行 一执行就死....\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1364740}, {"id": 283981, "content": "讨论的本身已经脱离了问题的本身 上升到个人 问题已经不再重要 重要的是个人的对错", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1350056}, {"id": 283982, "content": "会议纪要", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 779602}, {"id": 284750, "content": "真正会议主旨三分钟，各种无关主旨一小时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1322091}, {"id": 283983, "content": "领导好不容易讲完了，每次主持人最后还要把领导的讲话重复一遍", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1355606}, {"id": 283984, "content": "每次开会领导画大饼的时候，询问你的意见又没有下文，提出的意见又被否认，更甚者还会责怪你没有团队精神。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1357492}, {"id": 283985, "content": "只画大饼，不干实事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1357492}, {"id": 283986, "content": "临场突发的完全让人懵逼的小活动", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 818716}, {"id": 289363, "content": "宋翼是我老公? forever~", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1363812}, {"id": 289364, "content": "刚刚是韩灵小可爱?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1363812}, {"id": 283989, "content": "强行例会可以说是最惨的，没啥好说的时候明明可以快速跳过，非得强行续个一两小时", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156796}, {"id": 283990, "content": "会议要有明确的议题，会议讨论的结果", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1357544}, {"id": 284247, "content": "听老板不断重复说自己的当年勇，哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1358721}, {"id": 283993, "content": "明明是需求调研会，业主非说“你定”", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 597684}, {"id": 283995, "content": "废话太多，不相关的产品线全在一起听着不懂不相关的事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819077}, {"id": 283996, "content": "没计划没重点，天马行空越扯越远。跟自己相关的内容就一分钟，也被扯着大家一起听两小时。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 856539}]}